{"parse":{"title":"Raw Redgill","pageid":44840,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|||4}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_06\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=13758\n|charges=1\n|ilvl=45\n|name=Raw Redgill\n|level=35\n|effect=Use: Restores 810 health over 27 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n==Source==\nThis item can be fished in numerous places, including [[Un'goro Crater]], [[Silithus]], [[Western Plaguelands]], [[Zul'gurub]], [[Azshara]], [[Felwood]], Echo Isles and [[Moonglade]].\n\n==Raw Redgill as an ingredient==\n=== Cooking ===\n \n* {{loot|Common|Filet of Redgill}}\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13758}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_redgill.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common items]]"}}}